_sText: I got board one night and started another map. I just went with the flow again. This is only 2-3 days of work. A preview of the construction can be found here. Youtube time lapse. There are two versions of this map. This is the snow version that has it snowing with snow on the ground and the other one has it raining. Teams spawn on opposite sides of the map. The layout is balanced to where both sides are identical but the trees are a bit off. The lower level of the map has crates and a small water area. Zip file includes .nav file
